        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer497992399" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17947205889417255203">Aunt Daisy nightmare is bloody and disturbing, but when she finally see who is involved, she sets in motion a unpredictable outcome of this who-done-it. Charlie Moon is on the case and worried for many reasons. One awesome read.</span>

